WEBVTT

00:04:29.560 --> 00:04:33.856
So the key for me was to translate
this feeling of walking on a staircase

00:04:33.880 --> 00:04:35.280
back to flat land.

00:04:35.880 --> 00:04:38.816
And a lot of ideas
were tested and tried on him,

00:04:38.840 --> 00:04:42.360
but the one that finally worked
was this one. Let's take a look.

00:04:45.440 --> 00:04:48.496
(Laughter)

00:04:48.520 --> 00:04:52.976
(Applause)

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:54.456
He walked faster, right?

00:04:54.480 --> 00:04:57.680
(Applause)

00:04:59.240 --> 00:05:02.016
I call this the staircase illusion,